cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the global log level to an invalid value 'invalid_level' will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent the DU from starting properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將全域日誌級別設定為無效值 'invalid_level'，會導致配置解析錯誤，並阻止 DU 正確啟動。
